["addation_2f5e310fa777693c"] = "The giraffe doesn\'t miss a thing, always in complete control of its surroundings, acting as the perfect "look-out" companion for heisting in the animal kingdom. Whatever it is, you\'ll see it coming miles away and the cops can forget to take you by surprise.", 
["addation_66e8f71f56449eba"] = "For a thousand years, the traveller slept, biding his time until the stars did align and a mortal of sufficient ability would unlock him from his unholy prison. Rejoice! For that day has come. Wield this power... wisely.", 
