["addation_971408e0516023c4"] = "Peter is a true legend and has been so for like, forever. A beast with a large, pointed, spiraling horn projected from its forehead, Peter is known by all of mankind as the go-to guy whenever you need to touch the rainbow. No, touch it. Touch the motherfucking rainbow. Now taste it.$NL;$NL;Shh. It\'s OK. You did good.", 
["addation_201b1fddd4615f95"] = "Vincent", 
["addation_5ecb2076c1601be0"] = "Vincent the Velociraptor and his best friend Andreas H\xc3\xa4ll Penninger the Protoceratops were out and about one day in the jungle when they got in a fight. It wasn\'t a big thing really but Vincent just wouldn\'t let it go. Andreas, being the stubborn Protoceratops he was, continued to mouth off to Vincent. Violent fighting ensued and to this day, no one is sure who actually won.", 
