["addation_307a6793764ae60a"] = "The Zombie", 
["addation_5f61fc08aba793db"] = "You lock your eyes on your prize until they water. Unattended, your slacking jaw lets slip a drop of saliva onto the floor as the need for possession takes over. The person you pine for is an object, the object is a person. It matters not, to your blinded senses.", 
["addation_5110838f25128775"] = "Why bother? Let the universe expand, die and grow dark. You have endless time to lift your fingers in protest at whatever mindless chore that demands you exert yourself in the slightest. Your life energy oozes from your soul, wasted and dissolved in the emptiness as you remain perpetually drained of ambition.", 
["addation_ee156988142b2826"] = "You are unbreakable. The ship is filling with water, but you refuse to move. Such are your principles that you would rather go into the deep with a failing institution than admit your folly and admit yourself as fallible as your peers. Justice is what you deem it to be, and damned be those who would oppose your righteous wisdom.", 
